Run yarn install / npm install first
add files: 

.env
.env.dev
.env.prod

with structure:

SLATE_STORE= STORE.myshopify.com

SLATE_PASSWORD= Private APP password

SLATE_THEME_ID= theme id, choose correct one

SLATE_IGNORE_FILES=

Insert Shopify path and credentials

Run yarn start/watch to start working on developer theme (env.dev)
Run yarn deploy to deploy to production theme (env.prod)
Check package.json for other commands